Release 0.9.3 - 2014-01-28

Type Changes By
Choose known types in serialization carefully. Reduce the set from v0.9.2 as that set of types was too large. Fixes #46. scolebourne
Fix BeanComparisonError. Fixes #45. scolebourne

Release 0.9.2 - 2014-01-27

Type Changes By
Remove encodeClass/decodeClass from main serialization API. Fixes #44. scolebourne
Handle refactored beans in deserialization. Fixes #43. scolebourne
BasicBeanBuilder get(String) returns builder rather than the requested data. Backwards incompatible, but the old code is useless so will never have been used. Fixes #42. scolebourne
Ensure XML reader property closed. Fixes #41. scolebourne
Handle type renames in deserialization. Fixes #40. scolebourne
Short types flag not being used in JodaBeanSer. Fixes #39. scolebourne

Release 0.9.1 - 2014-01-20

Type Changes By
Fix immutable collection copies to preserve comparators. Affects SortedSet and SortedMap. Fixes #37. scolebourne
Remove incorrect suppress unchecked in immutable generic beans. Fixes #38. scolebourne

Release 0.9.0 - 2013-12-14

Type Changes By
Support partially final beans and immutable subclasses. This support is complex and not recommended, but sometimes necessary. Fixes #24. scolebourne
Recreate XMLInputFactory each time due to JDK bug JDK-8028111. Fixes #36. scolebourne
Fix to ensure nested class constructors are private if the type is final. May cause beans to regenerate. Fixes #35. scolebourne
Extend notNull validation to collection properties. May cause beans to regenerate. Fixes #34. scolebourne
Enhance PropertyStyle. Add isReadOnly(). Fixes #33. scolebourne
Add 'equalIgnoring' utility to compare two beans ignoring one or more properties. Fixes #32. scolebourne

Release 0.8.6 - 2013-11-06

Type Changes By
XML generation of beans with no fields broken. Affected COMPACT mode, not PRETTY mode. Fixes #30. scolebourne
FlexiMap should retain the order of properties. Use LinkedHashMap not HashMap. Fixes #31. scolebourne

Release 0.8.5 - 2013-10-22

Type Changes By
Fix code generation unchecked annotation when no writable properties. scolebourne
Allow beans to have two generic type parameters. Fixes #21. scolebourne
Fix code generation of private immutable builders. Fixes #26. scolebourne
Parse trailing comments on property definitions. Fixes #27. scolebourne

Release 0.8.4 - 2013-10-14

Type Changes By
Add setting to allow immutable builders to be private. Fixes #26. scolebourne
Avoid code generating two lines next to one another. scolebourne
Handle extra spaces in class/extends definitions. Fixes #25. scolebourne
Fix code generation for properties of generic type array. Where bean is Foo<T> and property is T[]. Also where immutable bean and property is T. Fixes #22. scolebourne
Bean toString should process arrays correctly. Fixes #23. scolebourne
Enhance handling of non-null and non-empty fields especially in immutable beans. See #20. scolebourne

Release 0.8.3 - 2013-10-09

Type Changes By
Immutable beans should handle nullable fields. Fixes #20. scolebourne
Generate an immutable bean with no properties correctly. scolebourne
Handle classes that are loaded but not initialized. Fixes #19. scolebourne

Release 0.8.2 - 2013-10-04

Type Changes By
Fix XML parsing of complex map entries. scolebourne
Handle multi-line class definition. Fixes #17. scolebourne
Fix FlexiBean serialization. Fixes #18. scolebourne
SerIteratorFactory off by one bug. scolebourne

Release 0.8.1 - 2013-10-03

Type Changes By
XML format no longer encodes tabs and newlines in elements. scolebourne
Allow private getters/setters using PropertyDefinition. scolebourne
Rename XML format map items to 'entry'. Allow map keys to be beans, using two 'item' elements beneath 'entry'. scolebourne
Extend analysis of collection/map generic types. scolebourne
Allow short types to be switched off. scolebourne
Handle simple types better when defined by unknown interface. scolebourne
Generate correct Javadoc for builder static method with generics. scolebourne
Allow known types to be built up during serialization. scolebourne
Permit XML format to omit root type. scolebourne
Output Joda-Convert data whenever available. scolebourne

Release 0.8 - 2013-09-30

Type Changes By
Move to OSGi generation via Maven plugin. scolebourne
Add XML round-trip serialization. Fixes #16. Allows the bean to be converted to and from XML in a human readable format. scolebourne
Enhance FlexiBean and MapBean. Fixes #15. These now work more like the original intention. Properties are always created on demand. FlexiBean property names are now validated to a minimal format. scolebourne
Identify Derived and Immutable properties at runtime. Fixes #14. Rename readWrite() to style() and PropertyReadWrite to ProperyStyle. Some existing beans may regenerate. scolebourne
Generate final classes for final beans. Fixes #13. Some existing beans may regenerate. scolebourne
Parse annotations above @PropertyDefinition as well as those below. Fixes #10. Some existing beans may regenerate. scolebourne
Add support for clone on beans.. Fixes #12. All existing beans will regenerate. scolebourne
Add support for immutable beans. Fixes #11. All existing beans will regenerate. scolebourne
Move location of equals/hashCode/toString methods in generation. All existing beans will regenerate. scolebourne
Allow generated beans to implement interface, rather than extend class. Fixes #9. Move propertyGet/propertySet/validate into meta-bean All existing beans will regenerate. scolebourne
Generate toString() methods. Fixes #8. All existing beans will regenerate. scolebourne
Optimize performance of generated equals for primitive numbers. Some existing beans will regenerate. scolebourne
Home page at GitHub. scolebourne

Release 0.7.1 - 2013-07-22

Type Changes By
Adjust code generation so can reformat in Eclipse without changing generated code. Existing beans will regenerate, even though the only change is one blank line. scolebourne
Add checkstyle scolebourne
Change to use m2e Maven Eclipse scolebourne

Release 0.7 - 2013-02-20

Type Changes By
Fix indentation issue in metaPropertyMap field. Existing beans will regenerate, even though the only change is indentation. scolebourne
Refactor BeanCodeGen to allow it to be used from tools. scolebourne
Fix command line arguments - -v -> -verbose. scolebourne
